star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/cortial31000\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d30178772787e5afc3fff36f282acab1?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/cortial31000\">cortial31000</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 24, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>Superbe widget...\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Easy and Reliable</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/revkevdenver\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6bc5661f4716c9c2bcfe78049f181ea6?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/revkevdenver\">revkevdenver</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 23, 2016</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>I have used several calendar plugins. This is the best right out of the box, easy to set up, reliable, and great add ons if you need them.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Excellent plugin</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/chrisesh\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2bdc6965af2e2646055b2e961b1cb148?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/chrisesh\">chrisesh</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 22, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>This is a great plugin for managing an events calendar. Very user-friendly and customizable.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Just great!!</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/despachotres\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/26f8e16d83fd1de6e776d9af46a9279d?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/despachotres\">despachotres</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 22, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>A great plugin, with great functionality for free!!!!\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Sweet</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/bigzepfan\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d4a21c15cca4a02a43601eed43836b1b?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/bigzepfan\">bigzepfan</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 21, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>Finally, someone who understands scheduling and not ripping you off with lame software. Great plug in, great company!\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Didn&#039;t get any support for something simple</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">3.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-empty\"></div><div class=\"star star-empty\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/wanabrar\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4c58705f6dbb104c649c403b5524d4ec?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/wanabrar\">wanabrar</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 20, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>Was asking and waiting for 2 days to know how i could change some certain colours. Only left disappointed cuz my question gets ignored.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Pleasure to work with</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/rexak\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b3eb9a5a352109a2aa64b060420b4522?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/rexak\">RexAK (rexak)</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 18, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>So far, plenty of hooks and conforms to WP standards. Easy to customize and develop custom plugins for. So far.... :)\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>The only good looking calendar with google incorporation out there</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/mlgngrlbs\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/200db807f9f2f8d02fd97482cc3ec958?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/mlgngrlbs\">mlgngrlbs</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 18, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>This plugin is awesome. The implementation is easy and the default styling itself is very nice to look at.<br />\nUsing a google calendar as source is not only easy with this plugin, it\'s also very well explained how to set it up.<br />\nWe are currently experiencing some problems with the implementation of the calendar widget, but since the support is very helpful, I would still rate it 5 stars.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:68:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/the-events-calendar.4.2.5.zip\";s:4:\"tags\";a:18:{s:8:\"calendar\";s:8:\"calendar\";s:5:\"class\";s:5:\"class\";s:7:\"concert\";s:7:\"concert\";s:10:\"conference\";s:10:\"conference\";s:4:\"date\";s:4:\"date\";s:5:\"dates\";s:5:\"dates\";s:5:\"event\";s:5:\"event\";s:6:\"events\";s:6:\"events\";s:11:\"google-maps\";s:11:\"google maps\";s:7:\"meeting\";s:7:\"meeting\";s:12:\"modern-tribe\";s:12:\"modern tribe\";s:9:\"organizer\";s:9:\"Organizer\";s:7:\"seminar\";s:7:\"seminar\";s:6:\"summit\";s:6:\"summit\";s:5:\"tribe\";s:5:\"tribe\";s:5:\"venue\";s:5:\"venue\";s:6:\"widget\";s:6:\"widget\";s:8:\"workshop\";s:8:\"workshop\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:18:\"http://m.tri.be/29\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:4:\"high\";s:69:\"//ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/banner-1544x500.png?rev=1449388\";s:3:\"low\";s:68:\"//ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=1449388\";}}','no'),(280829,'_transient_timeout_d343615f5241ecd5b21fd8a4eb817c7c','1472257929','no'),(280831,'_site_transient_timeout_browser_d71ff4a3c3a327d11c8c44da1209196e','1472859423','yes'),(280832,'_site_transient_browser_d71ff4a3c3a327d11c8c44da1209196e','a:9:{s:8:\"platform\";s:5:\"Linux\";s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"Firefox\";s:7:\"version\";s:4:\"48.0\";s:10:\"update_url\";s:23:\"http://www.firefox.com/\";s:7:\"img_src\";s:50:\"http://s.wordpress.org/images/browsers/firefox.png\";s:11:\"img_src_ssl\";s:4